Hello everyone! This is Isaac, I am the composer and producer of this EP. It is a higher priority to me that people experience my music over anything else. With that said there are in fact many ways you can support without even spending a single penny. And even some ways by doing just that. If you download I do ask you read this whole description box. 

The first thing I ask is you share my Soundcloud and or Bandcamp link on your Facebook saying what you think of my music. You can find those here: 

Soundcloud: http://snd.sc/18m9PhM - Most of my stuff is free unlike the EP
